{"id": "cpos007", "name": "Audio_RuinZone_702_11_25", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Machine_Gun_Reverb", "Machine Gun"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Any questions? This is more or less how it feels. Look, all within the center circle. Understood?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Nope, not at all. By the way, don't people generally begin their practice with handguns? What's all this about? Showing off?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Haha, yep. Here, this one's for you.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Don't point the barrel at people...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Rest assured. These are all rubber bullets. Their trajectory will be a little lower than real bullets. Raise your hands... That's right, just like this.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Does this count as you trying to molest me?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Why would I want to molest a skinny boy like you? Now pull the trigger.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "Gunshot"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... Huh, turns out you're quite talented at this!\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "It feels pretty much the same as the games we used to play.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Ah! So you were going easy on me back then after all? Interesting, let's have a match!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "A match of what...? You want to start a gunfight here?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "A target practice match, you dumba**! Getting hit by these bullets still hurts like hell, you know?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "Gunshot"], "content": ""}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Speaking of which... you really used that guy's money to buy all this stuff.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "He told us to use it, so why not. Besides, he has a good point. You really need to learn how to protect yourself. Or else you'd be a complete liability when we're in action.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Don't forget who's the one that saved you back in the underground tunnels.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "If I have to rely on your slow as f*** GAMEBAI, I can have infinite lives and it still won't be enough.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "Gunshot"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Judging from the number of bullseyes, my accuracy is a lot better than yours, isn't it? There's no point in practicing at all.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Idiot. Fire the shots consecutively. Empty this magazine.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "Consecutive Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......?\n... The last few shots didn't even hit the target...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "A real gun's recoil, weight, and the delay between each shot are all nowhere near as stable as they are in games. How do you feel? Your arms are starting to feel sore, right? What you just used is the smallest gun we have here too.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Did you forget what you told me when you were teaching me how to play the guitar? The \"Empty Glass Mentality\", never be boastful just because you have a little experience or talent.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... I just made that stuff up on the fly. However, your guitar skills did indeed improve greatly afterward. Guess I can't complain then.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Good. Now let's continue.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "Consecutive Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Whew... This is a lot more exhausting than I thought.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Your stamina is way too low.\nKeep both feet as wide as your shoulders. Keep your back straight and don't hunch. Make sure your shoulders, elbows, and fingertips are on the same straight line. The moment you pull the trigger, relax your body as much as possible. This puts less stress on your body, thus it is less tiring.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "Gunshot"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "It really is...\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Hmph, I'm not a bad teacher, right?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Did Luis teach you all this?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "Consecutive Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "When I was little, because of some stupid reasons, I stole my father's gun. He gave me a serious beating after he found out.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "Consecutive Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "In all honesty, when we were stealing it, both Shannon and I were utterly terrified. We didn't even dare to disengage the safety. You were trained from a very young age by Luis, right? The first time you ever held a gun, did you feel as calm as you are now?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... Yeah. I don't think I was scared at all back then. All I thought about was that I'm helping out my father. Besides, the things we shot at were all machines too. He never assaulted a person...\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Except my father.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon...\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "Consecutive Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Only after actually holding one in my hands did I realize how heavy this thing is.\nThe force of the bullet being fired... felt so real.\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "If I were in Luis's position, what would I do? If it was to protect you... I would probably pull the trigger as well.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "However, how would it feel like then, when you realized that you've just killed a person?\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "Consecutive Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Must've felt like s***.\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... Yeah.\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "When you're firing a gun... you look as if you're on stage. Strong-willed, filled with confidence, and sometimes a little happy.\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... I won't lie to you anymore. Indeed, to me, this is another thing that allows me to acknowledge who I am...\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "After we broke up, I once tried to throw all my guns into the river. Yet in the end, I still couldn't let them go... That's the only place where I feel more alive than when I'm on stage. I never even once considered the consequences of those actions either... or should I say I pretended to not know for my own sake. I'm horrible, aren't I...?\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "If, like your music, you can use this ability to help more people, perhaps it's not that horrible... What you need to let go of is not guns... but the past.\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "Consecutive Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "See, all within the center circle. This counts as a passing grade, right?\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Machine_Gun_Reverb", "機関銃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "ど？とりあえずこんな感じ。\n見て。全部中心を貫いてる。\n分かった？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……全く分からない。\n普通は拳銃から練習し始めるもんじゃないのか？\nなんだこれは……ただの腕前自慢か？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "あはは、バレたか。\nほい、これあげる。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "銃口を人に向けるなよ……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "大丈夫だって。\n中身は全部ゴム弾だから、普通の弾に比べて下にズレやすい。\n腕を上に構えて……そう、その感じ。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "俺のことからかってるのか……？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "あんたなんかからかって何が面白いわけ？\n早く撃って。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……おーやるじゃん！\n意外と才能あるかもよ。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "昔ゲームでやった感覚とそんな変わらないな。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "あ！\nてか、あん時手抜いてたっしょ？\nふーん、面白いじゃん。勝負だ！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "勝負ってどうやってだ……？\n今からここで撃ち合いか？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "バカ！？\nこれで撃ったら痛いなんてもんじゃないんですけど？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "そういえばお前……あの人の金本当に使ったんだな。\nこれ買ったんだろ？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "使わなかったら無駄になるだけだし。\nあいつの言うことは正しい。\nあんたも自分の身を守る術くらい知ってた方がいい。\nじゃないとただの足手まといだっつの。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "地下で誰がお前を助けたか忘れるなよ。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "あんたのあのクソ遅いGAMEBAIに頼ってたんじゃ、命がいくつあっても足りないね。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "的を見た感じ、俺の方がお前よりも正確みたいだな？\n練習の必要はなさそうだ。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "バカ。もっと連続して撃って。\nこれ全部使いきるまで。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連続した銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\n……後半の弾が全然当たってない……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "本物の銃は反動も強いし、重みもある。\nあと毎回撃った時の時差も、ゲームみたいに安定してないわけ。\nど？手が疲れてきたんじゃない？\nあんたが使ってるのは一番小さいやつなんだけどねぇ。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "ギターを教えてくれた時のこと忘れた？\n経験や才能があるからって驕るな。ってね。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……あれは適当に言っただけだ。\nそれに、お前はあの後上達しただろ？\n何も言うことはない。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "素晴らしい。\nじゃ、続けるよ。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連続した銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "ハァ……結構きついな。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "あんたの体力がなさすぎるんだよ。\n両脚は肩幅、背筋は伸ばして！猫背にならない！\n肩、ひじ、指先は一直線！\n発射の瞬間は身体の力を抜いたほうがいい。\n余計な力を使わずに済む。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "本当だ……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "ふふん、さっすがあたし。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Luisさんがお前に教えたんだろ。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連続した銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "子供の時、父さんの銃を盗んだことがあって、思いっきり殴られた。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連続した銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "あの時は俺もShannonも恐ろしくてたまらなかったな。\nお前も、子供の頃からLuisさんに訓練されてたんだろ？\n初めて手にした時もそんなに冷静だったのか？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……うん。\n全く怖いって気持ちはなかった。\nただ、父さんの力になりたいってそれだけ。\n撃つ相手も人じゃなくてロボットだしね。\n父さんも人に対して撃ったことは……ない。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……俺の父親以外な。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連続した銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "ちゃんと手に持ってみてはじめて分かる。\nこいつの重さも、弾を撃つ時の感触も……リアルだ。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "もし俺がLuisさんの立場だったら、どうしてたんだろうな？\nお前を守るために……撃ってたと俺は思う。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "人を殺すってどんな感じなんだろうな。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連続した銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……きっと最悪な気分だ。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……うん。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "お前は、銃を撃ってる時もステージに立ってる時と同じで、自信にあふれた強い目をしてる。\nそれで、時々楽しそうな顔もする。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……もうあたしはあんたに嘘をつかない。\n確かに、銃を撃ってる時、あたしは自分に自信が持てる。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "あんたと別れて、一度は銃なんか全部川に捨てやるって思った。\nでも、捨てられなかった……\nだって、あたしはそこにいる時だけ、ステージに立ってる時よりも生きてるって感じることができるから。\n後のことなんて考えずに……\n自分のために知らん顔してるんだよ。\nあたし最低でしょ……\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "音楽みたいに、その力でより多くの人を救えるなら、そこまで最低じゃない……お前が手放すべきなのは……過去だ。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連続した銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "見ろ。\n全部中心に当たったぞ。\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Machine_Gun_Reverb", "機槍"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "如何？大概就是這種感覺，看吧，全在中心內。懂了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……完全不懂。一般都是從手槍開始練習吧？這是怎樣？炫技？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "哈哈，答對了。來，這把給你。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "槍口別對著人……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "放心，這些都是橡膠彈，彈道會比實彈低一點。手抬高……對，像這樣。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……妳是在吃我豆腐嗎？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你這皮包骨有什麼好吃的？快開槍。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……哇，你還蠻有天份的嘛！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "跟我們以前玩遊戲的時候感覺差不多。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "啊！你那個時候果然偷放水了吧？有意思，我們來比賽！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "比什麼……？現在在這邊開打嗎？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "打靶啦！這打到人也是很痛的好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "是說……妳還真的用了那傢伙的錢買這些東西。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "不用白不用囉。他說得很對，你也真的是要學會自保才行，不然一點用場都派不上。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "別忘了在地下是誰救了妳。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "要靠你那慢得要死的 GAMEBAI 有幾條命都不夠。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "從靶心看起來我比妳準很多啊？根本沒有練習的必要。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "笨蛋，你連續多開幾槍，把這個彈夾打完。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\n……後面幾發全在靶外……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "真槍的後座力、重量還有每一發的擊發時差可不像遊戲那麼穩，怎樣？手開始酸了吧？你拿的還是最小把的咧。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你忘記教我吉他的時候自己說過什麼嗎？「空杯心態」，不要因為自己有一點經驗或天份就膨脹了。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……那只是隨口說說的。不過妳後來的確彈得很好，那我也沒有怨言了。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "很好，那繼續吧。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "呼……這真的不是一般的累啊。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "是你體力太差了。\n雙腳齊肩，背往前打直，不要駝背，肩膀、手肘、指尖呈直線，發射的瞬間身體盡量放鬆，這樣會比較省力。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "真的……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "哼哼，我教得不錯吧？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Luis 教妳這些的？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我小時候因為某些原因偷拿了我爸的執法槍，被他狠狠揍了一頓。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "其實拿著的時候我跟 Shannon 都很害怕，根本連保險都不敢關。妳也是從很小就被 Luis 訓練了吧？第一次拿槍的感覺，也是像現在這樣這麼冷靜嗎？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……嗯。當時好像完全沒有害怕的心情，心裡只想著能幫上爸爸的忙，畢竟要打的也都是機器。他從來沒有攻擊過人……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……除了我爸以外。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "實際拿過才知道，原來這東西這麼重，子彈射出時的力道……好真實。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "如果我站在 Luis 的立場會怎樣？為了保護妳……我也會開槍的吧。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "但知道自己殺了人又會是什麼感覺？\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……感覺肯定糟透了。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……嗯。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳開槍的時候……看起來就像在台上一樣，很堅定、充滿自信，偶爾有點開心。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……我不會再對你說謊，的確這對我來說是另一件能找到自我認同感的事情……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "我們分手後，我曾經把所有槍都丟進河裡，但後來還是放不下……只有在那個地方，讓我比在台上還更有活著的感覺，甚至也沒考慮過做那些事造成的後果……或著說為了自己裝作不知情，很差勁對吧……？\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "如果像音樂一樣，能用這份能力幫助更多人，或許也沒那麼差勁……妳要放下的是過去。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "看，全在中心內。這樣算及格了吧？\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Machine_Gun_Reverb", "기관총"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "어때? 대략 이런 느낌이야.\n잘 봐. 전부 중앙에 명중했지?\n이해할 수 있겠어?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...완전히 모르겠어. 처음 연습할 땐 보통은 권총으로 시작하는 거 아니야? 이건 그냥 네 실력 자랑하려고 보여준 거잖아...\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "하하하! 빙고~\n자, 이걸 줄게.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "총구는 사람한테 겨누지 말고...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "안심해. 이건 모두 고무탄이니까. 일반탄에 비해 탄도도 많이 낮아. 손가락을 올려서... 옳지, 이렇게.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...몰래 더듬지 마.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "만질 것도 없는 주제에!\n빨리 총이나 쏴봐.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "총성"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "...와! \n생각보다 재능이 있는 것 같은데!?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "예전에 건슈팅 게임했을 때랑 비슷한 느낌이군.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "앗! 역시 그때 너, 봐주면서 한 거였지!? \n다시 대결해!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "대결은 무슨... 여기서 바로 한 판?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "바보야!? \n실탄이 아니라도 맞으면 엄청 아프다고!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "기관총"], "content": ""}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "그런데... 정말로 그 녀석이 보내준 돈으로 이것들을 사 올 줄은...\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "쓰라고 줬는데 써야지 그럼. 그 녀석이 한 말이 맞아. 너도 네 몸 하나쯤은 간수할 줄 알아야지. 그렇지 않으면 발목만 잡게 될 테니까.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "지하에서 누가 널 구해줬는지 벌써 잊었어?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "그 느려터진 GAMEBAI 실력에 의지하다간 목숨 몇 개는 그냥 날아가버릴 거야.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "총성"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "과녁 중심엔 내가 더 많이 맞춘 것 같은데? 굳이 연습할 필요는 없을 것 같아.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "멍청아, 연사로 쏴보라고.\n이 탄창 다 쓸 때까지.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "연사"], "content": ""}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......?\n...뒤에 몇 발은 아예 과녁 바깥으로...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "진짜 총은 반동도 무게도 완전히 달라. 그리고 쏠 때마다 게임처럼 조준점이 안정적이지도 못해. 어때? 손이 조금씩 시리기 시작하지? 네가 든 것은 가장 작은 소형 총기에 속한다고.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "내게 기타를 가르쳐줬을 때 네가 한 말 기억하지? 자신의 경험과 재능만 믿고 자만하지 말라고 말이야.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...그땐 그냥 입에서 나오는 대로 한 말이라고. 그래도 결국은 기타 실력이 월등히 좋아지긴 했지... 나도 불평은 말아야겠군.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "아주 좋은 태도군.\n그럼 계속해보자.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "연사"], "content": ""}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "휴... 이거, 보통 피곤한 게 아닌데...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "체력이 부족해서 그래.\n네 체력이 너무 부족해.\n양 다리와 어깨를 벌리고 허리를 펴!\n어깨, 팔꿈치, 손끝은 일직선으로!\n그리고 발사하는 순간 몸에 힘을 살짝 빼고. 이러면 여분의 힘을 남겨둘 수 있어.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "총성"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "정말이군...\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "후훗! 어때? 내가 가르쳐주니까?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Luis 씨가 가르쳐줬었어?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "연사"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "어렸을 때 어떤 이유로 아버지의 총을 훔친 적이 있었어. 그땐 정말 반죽음이 되도록 얻어맞았지.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "연사"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "사실 총을 처음 쥐었을 때, 나와 Shannon은 엄청 겁을 먹었었지... 넌 어렸을 때부터 Luis 씨한테 훈련을 받았지? 처음 총을 쥐었을 때, 침착할 수 있었어? 지금처럼?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "....응. \n그땐 무섭다는 느낌은 전혀 들지 않았었어. 그저 아빠를 돕고 싶다는 마음만 가득했으니까. 그리고 쏴야 할 목표들 역시 기계들이었고. 아빠는 한 번도 사람을 향해 총을 쏜 적이 없어...\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...내 아버지 빼고 말이지...\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon......\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "연사"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "실제로 쏴보면 알게 돼. 이 무게... 그리고 총알이 나가고 난 후에 반동... 진짜 총을 쏠 때의 느낌...\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "만약 내가 Luis 씨의 입장이었다면 어땠을까? \n널 지키기 위해... 나도 총을 쐈을 거야...\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "하지만 자신의 손으로 사람을 죽인 느낌이 어떤 건지도 알게 되겠지.\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "연사"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...분명 최악의 느낌일 거야.\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": ".......응\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "너는 총을 쏠 때, 꼭 무대 위에서의 모습과 비슷해. 확고한  자신감에 찬 모습... 어쩔 땐 즐거워 보이기까지 하니까.\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "...네게 또다시 거짓말하고 싶지 않으니까 솔직히 말할게. 네 말대로 총을 쏠 때 어떤 자신감이 생기곤 해.\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "우리가 헤어졌을 때, 가지고 있던 모든 총들을 전부 강에다 던져버리려고 했는데 그러지 못했지... 무대 위에 있을 때보다 총을 쏘고 있을 때야말로 내가 살아있다는 것을 더 실감했던 것 같아. 심지어 뒷감당은 내 알바 아니라는 식으로 느끼기까지 했으니... 나 정말 최악이지?\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "네 음악처럼, 이 능력도 누군가를 돕는데 사용할 수 있다면 최악은 아닐 거다... 네가 놓아줘야 할 것은 총이 아닌, 네 과거야.\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "연사"], "content": ""}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "전부 가운데 명중했다.\n이 정도면 합격이겠지?\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Machine_Gun_Reverb", "機槍"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "如何？大概就是這種感覺，看吧，全在中心內。懂了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……完全不懂。一般都是從手槍開始練習吧？這是怎樣？炫技？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "哈哈，答對了。來，這把給你。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "槍口別對著人……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "放心，這些都是橡膠彈，彈道會比實彈低一點。手抬高……對，像這樣。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……妳是在吃我豆腐嗎？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你這皮包骨有什麼好吃的？快開槍。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……哇，你還蠻有天份的嘛！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "跟我們以前玩遊戲的時候感覺差不多。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "啊！你那個時候果然偷放水了吧？有意思，我們來比賽！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "比什麼……？現在在這邊開打嗎？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "打靶啦！這打到人也是很痛的好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "是說……妳還真的用了那傢伙的錢買這些東西。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "不用白不用囉。他說得很對，你也真的是要學會自保才行，不然一點用場都派不上。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "別忘了在地下是誰救了妳。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "要靠你那慢得要死的 GAMEBAI 有幾條命都不夠。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "從靶心看起來我比妳準很多啊？根本沒有練習的必要。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "笨蛋，你連續多開幾槍，把這個彈夾打完。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\n……後面幾發全在靶外……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "真槍的後座力、重量還有每一發的擊發時差可不像遊戲那麼穩，怎樣？手開始酸了吧？你拿的還是最小把的咧。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你忘記教我吉他的時候自己說過什麼嗎？「空杯心態」，不要因為自己有一點經驗或天份就膨脹了。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……那只是隨口說說的。不過妳後來的確彈得很好，那我也沒有怨言了。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "很好，那繼續吧。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "呼……這真的不是一般的累啊。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "是你體力太差了。\n雙腳齊肩，背往前打直，不要駝背，肩膀、手肘、指尖呈直線，發射的瞬間身體盡量放鬆，這樣會比較省力。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "真的……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "哼哼，我教得不錯吧？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Luis 教妳這些的？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我小時候因為某些原因偷拿了我爸的執法槍，被他狠狠揍了一頓。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "其實拿著的時候我跟 Shannon 都很害怕，根本連保險都不敢關。妳也是從很小就被 Luis 訓練了吧？第一次拿槍的感覺，也是像現在這樣這麼冷靜嗎？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……嗯。當時好像完全沒有害怕的心情，心裡只想著能幫上爸爸的忙，畢竟要打的也都是機器。他從來沒有攻擊過人……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……除了我爸以外。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "實際拿過才知道，原來這東西這麼重，子彈射出時的力道……好真實。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "如果我站在 Luis 的立場會怎樣？為了保護妳……我也會開槍的吧。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "但知道自己殺了人又會是什麼感覺？\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……感覺肯定糟透了。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……嗯。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳開槍的時候……看起來就像在台上一樣，很堅定、充滿自信，偶爾有點開心。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……我不會再對你說謊，的確這對我來說是另一件能找到自我認同感的事情……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "我們分手後，我曾經把所有槍都丟進河裡，但後來還是放不下……只有在那個地方，讓我比在台上還更有活著的感覺，甚至也沒考慮過做那些事造成的後果……或著說為了自己裝作不知情，很差勁對吧……？\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "如果像音樂一樣，能用這份能力幫助更多人，或許也沒那麼差勁……妳要放下的是過去。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "看，全在中心內。這樣算及格了吧？\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Machine_Gun_Reverb", "机枪"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "如何？大概就是这种感觉，看吧，全在中心内。懂了吗？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……完全不懂。一般都是从手枪开始练习吧？这是怎样？炫技？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "哈哈，答对了。来，这把给你。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "枪口别对着人……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "放心，这些都是橡胶弹，弹道会比实弹低一点。手抬高……对，像这样。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……妳是在吃我豆腐吗？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你这皮包骨有什么好吃的？快开枪。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "枪声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……哇，你还蛮有天份的嘛！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "跟我们以前玩游戏的时候感觉差不多。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "啊！你那个时候果然偷放水了吧？有意思，我们来比赛！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "比什么……？现在在这边开打吗？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "打靶啦！这打到人也是很痛的好吗？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "枪声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "是说……妳还真的用了那家伙的钱买这些东西。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "不用白不用啰。他说得很对，你也真的是要学会自保才行，不然一点用场都派不上。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "别忘了在地下是谁救了妳。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "要靠你那慢得要死的 GAMEBAI 有几条命都不够。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "枪声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "从靶心看起来我比妳准很多啊？根本没有练习的必要。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "笨蛋，你连续多开几枪，把这个弹夹打完。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "连续枪声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\n……后面几发全在靶外……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "真枪的后座力、重量还有每一发的击发时差可不像游戏那么稳，怎样？手开始酸了吧？你拿的还是最小把的咧。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你忘记教我吉他的时候自己说过什么吗？ 「空杯心态」，不要因为自己有一点经验或天份就膨胀了。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……那只是随口说说的。不過妳后来的确弹得很好，那我也没有怨言了。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "很好，那继续吧。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "连续枪声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "呼……这真的不是一般的累啊。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "是你体力太差了。\n双脚齐肩，背往前打直，不要驼背，肩膀、手肘、指尖呈直线，发射的瞬间身体尽量放松，这样会比较省力。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "枪声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "真的……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "哼哼，我教得不错吧？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Luis 教妳这些的？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "连续枪声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我小时候因为某些原因偷拿了我爸的执法枪，被他狠狠揍了一顿。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "连续枪声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "其实拿着的时候我跟 Shannon 都很害怕，根本连保险都不敢关。妳也是从很小就被 Luis 训练了吧？第一次拿枪的感觉，也是像现在这样这么冷静吗？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……嗯。当时好像完全没有害怕的心情，心里只想着能帮上爸爸的忙，毕竟要打的也都是机器。他从来没有攻击过人……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……除了我爸以外。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "连续枪声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "实际拿过才知道，原来这东西这么重，子弹射出时的力道……好真实。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "如果我站在 Luis 的立场会怎样？为了保护妳……我也会开枪的吧。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "但知道自己杀了人又会是什么感觉？\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "连续枪声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……感觉肯定糟透了。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……嗯。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳开枪的时候……看起来就像在台上一样，很坚定、充满自信，偶尔有点开心。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……我不会再对你说谎，的确这对我来说是另一件能找到自我认同感的事情……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "我们分手后，我曾经把所有枪都丢进河里，但后来还是放不下……只有在那个地方，让我比在台上还更有活着的感觉，甚至也没考虑过做那些事造成的后果……或着说为了自己装作不知情，很差劲对吧……？\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "如果像音乐一样，能用这份能力帮助更多人，或许也没那么差劲……妳要放下的是过去。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "连续枪声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "看，全在中心内。这样算及格了吧？\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}